                "description": "Specifies the mode of authentication method enabled for this service. A value of <code>SERVICE_MANAGED</code> means that you are using this file transfer protocol-enabled server to store and access user credentials within the service. A value of <code>API_GATEWAY</code> indicates that you have integrated an API Gateway endpoint that will be invoked for authenticating your user into the service."
