                "description": "<p>One of the available step types.</p> <ul> <li> <p> <i>Copy</i>: copy the file to another location</p> </li> <li> <p> <i>Custom</i>: custom step with a lambda target</p> </li> <li> <p> <i>Delete</i>: delete the file</p> </li> <li> <p> <i>Tag</i>: add a tag to the file</p> </li> </ul>"
